Hello, Bonjour

This is css_unicassault for Css , based on my cs_unicassault map for Cs15/16.

Many possibilities in this map to access to hostages; many palces to be hidden, roof acces, vent access, ladder, underground, crates and vehicles...

Enjoy it !!!
